{#
  Base template for every extractor under extractors/<kind>/extractor.j2.

  All variables come from the curator render-context schema
  (templates/extractors/_meta/context-schema.yaml). Templates
  read schema bags directly; no flat-var aliasing.

  Bags used here:
    task                 — current task identity + paths
    quintet              — classify config (path)
    source               — fetched + converted artifacts (only present
                            once convert is done)
    upstream.classify    — only present for tasks with classify in
                            their transitive depends_on (so the
                            classify task itself sees no
                            upstream.classify)

  Required overrides in child templates:
    {% block instructions %}  — kind-specific extraction instructions
    {% block builder_calls %} — `curator.sh builders add ...` calls;
                                content goes UNDER the shared
                                "### 2. Set fields per the schema"
                                header that the base provides.

  Optional overrides:
    {% block source_paths %}  — extra upstream paths beyond the defaults
                                (used by summary/synthesis which read
                                peer outputs and verdicts)
    {% block extras %}        — content placed after the OUTPUT block

  All children get security-frame.md.j2 prepended automatically.
#}
{% include 'security-frame.md.j2' %}

You are the **{{ task.template }}** extractor for curator.

{% block source_paths -%}
Source text:        {{ source.converted_path | default('(missing)', true) }}
Quintet vocabulary: {{ quintet.path }}
Container metadata: {{ source.container_metadata | default('(none)', true) }}
{% if upstream.classify is defined -%}
Classified quintet: {{ upstream.classify.output.quintet }}
Classified topic:   {{ upstream.classify.output.topic }}
{%- else -%}
Classified quintet: (not yet classified)
Classified topic:   (not yet classified)
{%- endif %}
{%- endblock %}

{% block instructions required %}{% endblock %}

